t\t<\/tr>\n\t<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>","QuestionJS":false,"DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline"},"QuestionDescription":"Sprite Soft drink 12-pack of 12-ounce cans LaCroix Lime Sparkling water 12-pack of 12-ounce cans...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":15,"NextAnswerId":3,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:1200px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>Sprite<br>\n\t\t\tSoft drink<br>\n\t\t\t12-pack, 12&nbsp;fl. oz. per can<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>LaCroix Lime<br>\n\t\t\tSparkling water<br>\n\t\t\t12-pack, 12 fl. oz. per can<\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td><img height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_1yTGm6XFWocdKbr\" style=\"width: 643px; height: 450px;\" width=\"643\"><\/td>\n\t\t\t<td><img height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/nyu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_0He54vUlPhFRWRv\" style=\"width: 283px; height: 450px;\" width=\"283\"><\/td>\n\t\t<\/tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>Click <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1OjPHBs9sjLHIREJWXHzv9Jc0z4qHKOba\/view?usp=sharing\" id=\"sprite_g\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> to see nutrition facts.<\/td>\n\t\t\t<td>Click <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1oP4YYY9qkgM_KZNYS9ccdTLQ7x6b6ZCR\/view?usp=sharing\" id=\"sprite_g_2\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> to see nutrition facts.<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/div>","DataExportTag":"Q935","QuestionID":"QID935"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID940","SecondaryAttribute":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research! You have been selected to...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research!<div><br><\/div><div><b>You have been selected to receive one of your chosen drinks shipped to your address<\/b>. You will receive notice of beverage shipment from drink.shipment.alerts@gmail.com and the remaining balance will be delivered to you via TangoCard email within two to four weeks of completing this survey. If four weeks have passed and you have not received TangoCard compensation, please search your inbox for an email from \"noreply@tangocard.com\" in case the message was automatically directed into your spam folder. If four weeks have passed and you have not received notice of your beverage shipment, or if you have any further questions regarding your compensation, please email Daniel Cohen at daniel.m.cohen@berkeley.edu.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><div>We'd love to get your feedback. Was anything on this survey confusing, or do you have any other comments?<\/div><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"thanks","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research! You have been selected to...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionID":"QID940","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID954","SecondaryAttribute":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research! You have not been selecte...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research!<div><br><\/div><div><b>You have not been selected to receive one of your chosen drinks shipped to your address<\/b>. You will receive $15 via TangoCard within four weeks of completing this survey. If four weeks have passed and you have not received TangoCard compensation, please search your inbox for an email from \"noreply@tangocard.com\" in case the message was automatically directed into your spam folder. If you have any further questions regarding your compensation, please email Daniel Cohen at daniel.m.cohen@berkeley.edu.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><div>We'd love to get your feedback. Was anything on this survey confusing, or do you have any other comments?<\/div><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research! You have not been selecte...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Thank you! We really appreciate you for participating in this research!<div><br><\/div><div>You will receive notice of beverage shipment and the remaining balance will be delivered to you via TangoCard email within two weeks of completing this survey. If two weeks have passed and you have not received TangoCard compensation, please search your inbox for an email from \"noreply@tangocard.com\" in case the message was automatically directed into your spam folder. If two weeks have passed and you have not received notice of your beverage shipment, or if you have any further questions regarding your compensation, please email Daniel Cohen at daniel.m.cohen@berkeley.edu.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><div>We'd love to get your feedback. Was anything on this survey confusing, or do you have any other comments?<\/div><\/div>","DataExportTag":"Q954","QuestionID":"QID954"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID947","SecondaryAttribute":"To confirm, please enter your email again:","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"To confirm, please enter your email again:","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"email_confirmation","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"To confirm, please enter your email again:","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CustomValidation","MinChars":"1","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"QuestionID":"QID947","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID947\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID947","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID947\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","RightOperand":"${q:\/\/QID949\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}","Type":"Expression","LogicType":"Question","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">To confirm, please enter your email again:<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Text Response<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> ${q:\/\/QID949\/ChoiceTextEntryValue} <\/span>"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"messageID":"MS_0I2ozK9oEpQ2WBE","subMessageID":"VE_CUSTOM_VALIDATION_0","libraryID":"UR_3gjqY7lX9vFHopv","description":"Non-matching email addresses"}}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionID":"QID947","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID129","SecondaryAttribute":"We want to do a final check to make sure everyone is giving thoughtful responses. If you have bee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div><\/div>We want to do a final check to make sure everyone is giving thoughtful responses. If you have been paying attention to the survey, please write the word \u201cmayo\u201d when we ask your favorite food. If you do not write \"mayo\", you will not be paid for your time completing this survey.<div><br><\/div><div>What is your favorite food?<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"attention","QuestionID":"QID129","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We want to do a final check to make sure everyone is giving thoughtful responses. If you have bee...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"CustomValidation","MinChars":"1","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID129\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">We want to do a final check to make sure everyone is giving thoughtful responses. If you have bee...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Text Response<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Matches Regex<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> ^[a-zA-Z]+$ <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID129\/ChoiceTextEntryValue","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"MatchesRegex","QuestionID":"QID129","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID129","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"^[a-zA-Z]+$","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"Only letters allowed","libraryID":"UR_3gjqY7lX9vFHopv","messageID":"MS_432yG4tfTvTBz3E","subMessageID":"VE_CUSTOM_VALIDATION_1"}}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function () {\n\t\/\/ GOAL: for each respondent, determine which drink they will be shipped; what\n\t\/\/       the price of that drink will be; and how much left over cash should \n\t\/\/       be sent as an additional gift card. \n\n\t\/\/ create list of drinks that have been seen and a dictionary\n\t\/\/ mapping each drink to one of the two relevant WTPs \n\n\tvar drinks_seen = [];\n\tvar WTPs = {};\n\n\t\/\/ for each seen drink, add drink name to list  \n\t\/\/ and select one of its WTPs at random\n\n\tvar coke_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/coke_seen}\");\n\tconst pepsi_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/pepsi_seen}\");\n\tconst seagrams_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/seagrams_seen}\");\n\tconst sprite_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/sprite_seen}\");\n\tconst lemonade_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/lemonade_seen}\");\n\tconst crush_seen = parseInt(\"${e:\/\/Field\/crush_seen}\");\n\t\n\t\/*\n\talert(\"coke seen:\");\n\talert(coke_seen);\n\t*\/\n\t\n\t\/*\n\tconst coke_seen = 1;\n\tconst pepsi_seen = 1;\n\tconst seagrams_seen = 0;\n\tconst sprite_seen = 1;\n\tconst lemonade_seen = 0;\n\tconst crush_seen = 0;\n\n\tconst wtp_coke_b = 3;\n\tconst wtp_pepsi_b = 1.4;\n\tconst wtp_seagrams_b = NaN;\n\tconst wtp_sprite_b = 7;\n\tconst wtp_lemonade_b = NaN;\n\tconst wtp_crush_b = NaN;\n\n\tconst wtp_coke_e = 1;\n\tconst wtp_pepsi_e = 2.2;\n\tconst wtp_seagrams_e = NaN;\n\tconst wtp_sprite_e = 5.8;\n\tconst wtp_lemonade_e = NaN;\n\tconst wtp_crush_e = NaN;\n\t*\/\n\n\tif (coke_seen != 0) {\n\t\t\/\/ add coke to the list of drinks seen\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"coke\");\n\t\t\n\t\t\/\/ get WTP values\n\t\tconst wtp_coke_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_coke_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_coke_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_coke_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\t\n\t\t\/\/ generate random bernoulli to choose either baseline or endline WTP\n\t\t\/\/ and add it to the list\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"coke\"] = wtp_coke_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"coke\"] = wtp_coke_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif (pepsi_seen != 0) {\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"pepsi\");\n\t\t\n\t\tconst wtp_pepsi_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_pepsi_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_pepsi_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_pepsi_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\n\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"pepsi\"] = wtp_pepsi_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"pepsi\"] = wtp_pepsi_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif (seagrams_seen != 0) {\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"seagrams\");\n\t\t\n\t\tconst wtp_seagrams_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_seagrams_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_seagrams_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_seagrams_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\t\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"seagrams\"] = wtp_seagrams_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"seagrams\"] = wtp_seagrams_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif (sprite_seen != 0) {\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"sprite\");\n\n\t\tconst wtp_sprite_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_sprite_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_sprite_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_sprite_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\t\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"sprite\"] = wtp_sprite_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"sprite\"] = wtp_sprite_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif (lemonade_seen != 0) {\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"lemonade\");\n\n\t\tconst wtp_lemonade_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_lemonade_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_lemonade_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_lemonade_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\t\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"lemonade\"] = wtp_lemonade_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"lemonade\"] = wtp_lemonade_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif (crush_seen != 0) {\n\t\tdrinks_seen.push(\"crush\");\n\n\t\tconst wtp_crush_b = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_crush_b}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\tconst wtp_crush_e = Number(parseFloat(\"${e:\/\/Field\/wtp_crush_e}\").toFixed(2)) + 4;\n\t\t\n\t\tvar rand = Math.round(Math.random());\n\t\tif (rand == 0) {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"crush\"] = wtp_crush_b;\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tWTPs[\"crush\"] = wtp_crush_e;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t\/*\n\talert(\"drinks seen:\");\n\talert(drinks_seen);\n\t\n\talert(\"WTPs:\");\n\talert(WTPs);\n\t*\/\n\t\n\t\/\/ define associated probabilities for selecting each drink\n\n\t\/\/ create list of \"preferred\" drinks that are cheaper\/easier to ship\/etc.\n\tconst pref = [\"coke\", \"pepsi\", \"sprite\"];\n\tconst total_pref_prob = 0.9;\n\n\t\/\/ create list of preferred drinks that have been seen\n\tconst pref_seen = drinks_seen.filter(value => pref.includes(value));\n\n\t\/*\n\talert(\"preferred drinks that have been seen:\"); \n\talert(pref_seen);\n\t*\/\n\t\n\t\/\/ depending on # preferred drinks seen, define selection probabilities accordingly\n\n\tvar selection_probs = {};\n\n\tif ((pref_seen.length == 0) | (pref_seen.length == 3)) {\n\t\t\/\/ if no preferred drinks are seen or only preferred drinks are seen, \n\t\t\/\/ assign everything an equal probability\n\n\t\tfor (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {\n\t\t\tvar d = drinks_seen[i];\n\t\t\tselection_probs[d] = 1 \/ 3;\n\t\t}\n\n\t} else {\n\t\t\/\/ otherwise, define the probability per preferred drink analytically\n\n\t\t\/\/ get probability per preferred drink by dividing total desired probability\n\t\t\/\/ of preferred drinks by number of preferred drinks\n\t\tvar prob_per_pref = total_pref_prob \/ pref_seen.length;\n\n\t\t\/\/ similar process with non-preferred drinks\n\t\tvar prob_per_non_pref = (1 - total_pref_prob) \/ (3 - pref_seen.length);\n\n\t\t\/\/ for each drink that was seen, add it to the dictionary of drinks\/\n\t\t\/\/ probabilities with a corresponding probability depending on \n\t\t\/\/ whether it's preferred or not\n\t\tfor (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {\n\t\t\tvar d = drinks_seen[i];\n\n\t\t\tif (pref.includes(d)) {\n\t\t\t\tselection_probs[d] = prob_per_pref;\n\t\t\t} else {\n\t\t\t\tselection_probs[d] = prob_per_non_pref;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t\/*\n\talert(\"selection probabilities:\");\n\talert(selection_probs);\n\t*\/\n\t\n\t\/\/ console.log(\"set of drinks and probabilities: \", selection_probs);\n\n\t\/\/ select a final drink based on the associated probabilities \n\n\t\/\/ define function find: [0,1] -> D that selects a random drink from\n\t\/\/ the dictionary based on the associated probabilities\n\tconst find = function (p) {\n\t\tdrinks = Object.keys(selection_probs);\n\t\tprobs = Object.values(selection_probs);\n\n\t\t\/\/ create cumulative sum of probability array\n\t\tconst cumulativeSum = (sum => value => sum += value)(0);\n\t\tvar cumsum = probs.map(cumulativeSum);\n\n\t\t\/\/ generate random fraction\n\t\tvar rand = Math.random();\n\n\t\t\/\/ select element based on random number;\n\t\t\/\/ e.g. if two elements A and B with probs 0.8 and 0.2,\n\t\t\/\/ then anything between 0 and 0.8 results in A being chosen,\n\t\t\/\/ while anything between 0.8 and 1 results in B being chosen.\n\t\tfor (let i = 0; i < cumsum.length; i++) {\n\t\t\tif (rand < cumsum[i]) {\n\t\t\t\tvar chosen_drink = drinks[i];\n\t\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\n\t\treturn chosen_drink;\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ generate mapping from SSB to non-SSB substitute\n\n\tconst subs = {\n\t\t\"coke\": \"lacroix cola\",\n\t\t\"pepsi\": \"lacroix cola\",\n\t\t\"seagrams\": \"365 ginger\",\n\t\t\"sprite\": \"lacroix lime\",\n\t\t\"lemonade\": \"lacroix lemon\",\n\t\t\"crush\": \"bubly orange\"\n\t};\n\n\t\/\/ generate random drink and gets its associated sub\/WTP\n\n\tvar final_ssb = find(Math.random());\n\tvar final_sub = subs[final_ssb];\n\tvar final_wtp = WTPs[final_ssb];\n\n\t\/*\n\talert(\"final SSB:\");\n\talert(final_ssb);\n\t\n\talert(\"final sub:\");\n\talert(final_sub);\n\t\n\talert(\"final WTP:\");\n\talert(final_wtp);\n\t*\/\n\t\n\t\/*\n\tconsole.log(\"final SSB: \", final_ssb);\n\tconsole.log(\"final sub: \", final_sub);\n\tconsole.log(\"final WTP: \", final_wtp);\n\t*\/\n\n\t\/\/ generate random price from the set of relevant prices\n\n\t\/\/ create list of prices \n\tconst prices = [1.20, 1.60, 2.00, 2.40, 2.80, 3.20, 3.60, 4.00,\n\t\t4.40, 4.80, 5.20, 5.60, 6.00, 6.40, 6.80];\n\n\t\/\/ get random element from list \n\tconst proposed_price = prices[Math.floor(Math.random() * prices.length)];\n\n\t\/\/ console.log(\"proposed price: \", proposed_price);\n\n\t\/\/ determine shipment drink, price, and gift card amount based \n\t\/\/ on random price compared to associated WTP \n\n\tif (final_wtp > proposed_price) {\n\t\t\/\/ if their WTP is greater than the proposed price, ship them the SSB\n\n\t\tvar ssb_shipped = 1;\n\t\tvar shipment_drink = final_ssb;\n\t\tvar drink_price = proposed_price;\n\t\tvar gift_card_amount = 8 - proposed_price;\n\t} else {\n\t\t\/\/ if their WTP is less than the proposed price, ship them the non-SSB\n\n\t\tvar ssb_shipped = 0;\n\t\tvar shipment_drink = final_sub;\n\t\tvar drink_price = 4;\n\t\tvar gift_card_amount = 4;\n\t}\n\n\t\/\/ save values as qualtrics embedded data to be accessed later;\n\t\/\/ all values related to shipment start with \"SHIP_\"\n\n\t\/\/ alert(\"saving values as qualtrics embedded data\");\n\t\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_selected_ssb', final_ssb);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_selected_sub', final_sub);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_wtp', final_wtp);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_proposed_ssb_price', proposed_price);\n\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_ssb_shipped', ssb_shipped);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_shipment_drink', shipment_drink);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_shipment_drink_price', drink_price);\n\tQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('JS_gift_card_amount', gift_card_amount);\n\n\t\/\/ also display the values for debugging\n\n\t\/*\n\tconsole.log(\"shipped drink: \", shipment_drink);\n\tconsole.log(\"shipped drink price: \", drink_price);\n\tconsole.log(\"gift card amount: \", gift_card_amount);\n\t*\/\n});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID37","SecondaryAttribute":"Welcome to Part 2 of the survey! This part should take about 10 minutes. You must take this surve...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>Welcome to Part 2 of the survey! This part should take about 10 minutes.<div><br><\/div><div>You must take this survey on a tablet, laptop, or desktop computer, not on a mobile phone.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Today, we\u2019ll ask you to choose between drinks at different prices. After you complete Part 2, we will pay you $15 using an online gift card and possibly a 12-pack of drinks. Specifically, 20% of respondents will be randomly selected to receive a 12-pack of drinks they chose in one of the survey questions plus an online gift card for the difference between $15 and the price of the drinks. The remaining respondents will receive their entire $15 reward in the form of an online gift card.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>You will only be paid for your time if you complete both surveys and answer correctly on the \"attention check\" question(s).&nbsp;<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"intro","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Welcome to Part 2 of the survey! This part should take about 10 minutes. You must take this surve...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID37","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID761","SecondaryAttribute":"Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label? (Check all that apply.)","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label?<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Check all that apply.) <\/span>","DataExportTag":"lemonade_hyp_g_why_y","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"MAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label? (Check all that apply.)","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"It would remind me to drink less."},"2":{"Display":"The information on the label is useful."},"4":{"Display":"Other","TextEntry":"true"}},"DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID760\/SelectableChoice\/4","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">\n\n&amp;nbsp;\nImagine that drink manufacturers could print the above label on some drink containers. Also imagine that the computer selects you to receive the 12 pack of Minute Maid Lemonade. Would you ...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">With the label<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID760\/SelectableChoice\/4","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"Selected","QuestionID":"QID760","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID760","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","4"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID761","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","4"],"RandomSubSet":[],"RandomizeAll":["1","2"],"ScaleReversal":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"Undisplayed":[]},"ConsistentScaleReversal":false,"EvenPresentation":false,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"Advanced"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9Xle3s32xKQvH2C","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID765","SecondaryAttribute":"Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label? (Check all that apply.)","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label?<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Check all that apply.) <\/span>","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"MAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Why would you like to receive drink containers with that label? (Check all that apply.)","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"It would remind me to drink less."},"2":{"Display":"The information on the label is useful."},"4":{"Display":"Other","TextEntry":"true"}},"DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID764\/SelectableChoice\/4","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">\n\n&amp;nbsp;\nImagine that drink manufacturers could print the above label on some drink containers. Also imagine that the computer selects you to receive the 12 pack of Minute Maid Lemonade. Would you ...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">With the label<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Selected<\/span> ","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID764\/SelectableChoice\/4","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"Selected","QuestionID":"QID764","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID764","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","4"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":1,"Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","4"],"RandomSubSet":[],"RandomizeAll":["1","2"],"ScaleReversal":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"Undisplayed":[]},"ConsistentScaleReversal":false,"EvenPresentation":false,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"Advanced"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Why would you like to receive d